        <item>
            <title>iPhone 16 爆假机事件，先达回收商蚀 3 万指生意难挨</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/09/22/iphone-16-4/mobile-phone/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=iphone-16-4</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/09/22/iphone-16-4/mobile-phone/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sun, 22 Sep 2024 05:00:06 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[手提电话]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[iPhone 16]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1264676</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>iPhone 16 系列日前正式开卖，先达广场内发生回收商收到假机的骗案，令其中一家店损失了高达 3 万元。涉事店家指出，这是开卖首日便发生的事件，回收的两部 iPhone 16 Pro Max 外观与真机极为相似，连盒内配件都非常完整，令店主慨叹「生意难做」。</p><p>一名店主在 Facebook 上分享了这宗骗案的详情，并附上假机的照片，两部手机的包装盒、配件及手机的外观都与真机几乎无异，难以分辨。这次事件令得主感到无奈，并表示手机市场的诈骗手法日益高明，回收商需更加谨慎。</p><p>据了解，该事件发生于旺角先达广场一间回收商店内。该店主表示，事发时因店舖人多拥挤，工作繁忙，未能即时仔细检查，导致收到两部假机，随后发现损失高达 3 万元。涉事店铺已立即报警处理。</p><p>警方接获报案后，根据初步调查结果，将案件列为「以欺骗手段取得财产」，并交由旺角刑事调查队第二队跟进调查。据悉，报案人称早前在西洋菜南街的另一商场内，以 24,000 元购入两部手机，并在亚皆老街另一商场打算转售时发现它们是样办机。至今警方尚未拘捕涉案人士，案件仍在调查中。</p><p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1264677" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/20240922115649-641x580.jpg" alt="" width="641" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/20240922115649-641x580.jpg 641w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/20240922115649.jpg 994w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 641px" /></p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1264678" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/460521946_9202849301-435x580.jpg" alt="" width="435" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/460521946_9202849301-435x580.jpg 435w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/460521946_9202849301.jpg 675w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 435px" /><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1264679" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/460630596_9202849667-435x580.jpg" alt="" width="435" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/460630596_9202849667-435x580.jpg 435w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/460630596_9202849667.jpg 675w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 435px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1264680" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/460722730_9202849267-435x580.j